kground: -ms-linear-gradient(left,#4D4D4D 0%,#D8D8D8 50%,#4D4D4D 100%);background: linear-gradient(left,#4D4D4D 0%,#D8D8D8 50%,#4D4D4D 100%);\"][vc_column][ultimate_carousel slide_to_scroll=\"single\" slides_on_mob=\"1\" arrow_color=\"#e44b6f\" arrow_size=\"36\" dots=\"off\"][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-uniF11D\" icon_size=\"40\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"Ubicación privilegiada\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"icon_\"]Sector Castropol<br />\r\nEl Poblado, Medellín[/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-uniF18A\" icon_size=\"40\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"Torre de 17 pisos\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"icon_\"]Con 28 apartamentos, dos apartamentos por piso[/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-uniF112\" icon_size=\"40\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"Piscinas climatizadas\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"icon_\"]Piscina, baño turco y solárium[/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-uniF140\" icon_size=\"40\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"125 m² de área construida\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"icon_\"]3 alcobas todas con baño, y la alcoba principal además con vestier y balcón[/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-uniF172\" icon_size=\"40\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"Cocina abierta\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"icon_\"]Se entrega con cubierta, campana y horno[/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-uniF133\" icon_size=\"40\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"Zonas comunes\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"icon_\"]Salón social, gimnasio, plazoleta de juegos infantiles, gimnasio semi dotado, zona BBQ[/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-uniF143\" icon_size=\"40\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"Dos ascensores\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"icon_\"]Para una mejor movilidad de los habitantes[/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-uniF15E\" icon_size=\"40\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"Parqueaderos para visitantes\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"icon_\"]Internos y con doble ruta de evacuación[/bsf-info-box][/ultimate_carousel][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"\" row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" angled_section=\"no\" text_align=\"left\" background_image_as_pattern=\"without_pattern\" full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" content_placement=\"middle\" css=\".vc_custom_1543076167087{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}\" el_id=\"video\"][vc_column][rev_slider alias=\"galicia\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"\" row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" angled_section=\"no\" text_align=\"left\" background_image_as_pattern=\"without_pattern\" bg_type=\"grad\" bg_override=\"full\" full_width=\"stretch_row\" equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"top\" el_id=\"descripcion\" bg_grad=\"background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0%, #8B2E59), color-stop(50%, #64214F), color-stop(100%, #8B2E59));background: -moz-linear-gradient(left,#8B2E59 0%,#64214F 50%,#8B2E59 100%);background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left,#8B2E59 0%,#64214F 50%,#8B2E59 100%);background: -o-linear-gradient(left,#8B2E59 0%,#64214F 50%,#8B2E59 100%);background: -ms-linear-gradient(left,#8B2E59 0%,#64214F 50%,#8B2E59 100%);background: linear-gradient(left,#8B2E59 0%,#64214F 50%,#8B2E59 100%);\" css=\".vc_custom_1547573047716{margin-top: -50px !important;border-bottom-width: 15px !important;padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;border-bottom-color: #e44b6f !important;border-bottom-style: solid !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"desc_text\"]El encanto que guarda el sector Castropol, en el Barrio Poblado de Medellín, tiene mucho que ver con los espacios que, sin saber por qué, quieres descubrir más. Y es que en su ambiente se respira tranquilidad, esa que sin necesidad de salir de la ciudad te hace sentir como si estuvieras fuera de ella. El sector atrapa a las almas que mejor disfrutan de buenas construcciones, amplias zonas verdes y poder salir a dar una caminata tranquila a cualquier hora del día.</p>\r\n<p>Nuestro proyecto está inspirado en las personas que gozan de gusto exquisito, quienes encuentran la definición de elegancia en la sutileza y aquellos que la vida les sabe mejor cuando se comparte acompañada de su familia en un perfecto espacio.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"desc_text\"]Nuestra torre Galicia la conforman 28 apartamentos, 19 pisos de altura y la seguridad de que al ingresar en ellos, estarás un poco más cerca al cielo. Espacios compartidos, acogedores, tranquilos, con prestigio innato y acabados de perfección, harán que tu historia vibre al ritmo de la emoción.</p>\r\n<p>¿Te decides venir a conocernos? ¡Te esperamos!<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"\" row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" angled_section=\"no\" text_align=\"left\" background_image_as_pattern=\"without_pattern\" full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" el_id=\"gal\" css=\".vc_custom_1543346522809{margin-top: -50px !important;}\"][vc_column][rev_slider alias=\"showcase-carousel\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"\" row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" angled_section=\"no\" text_align=\"left\" background_image_as_pattern=\"without_pattern\" css=\".vc_custom_1552754828837{padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"\" row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" angled_section=\"no\" text_align=\"left\" background_image_as_pattern=\"without_pattern\" full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"texto1\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" style=\"font-size: 26px; color: #642153; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; font-family: Raleway; font-weight: 500; font-style: normal;\"><strong>UBICACIÓN</strong> DEL PROYECTO</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_gmaps link=\"#E-8_\" size=\"300\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"\" row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" angled_section=\"no\" text_align=\"left\" background_image_as_pattern=\"without_pattern\" el_id=\"marca\"][vc_column][bsf-info-box icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^276|url^https://constructoraguigo.com/galicia/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/logo_guigo_sticky.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^logo_guigo_sticky|description^null\" img_width=\"200\" pos=\"right\" el_class=\"guigo\"]</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\">Prestigiosos <strong>proyectos de alto perfil</strong><br />\r\n<strong>en los sectores más exclusivos</strong> del Poblado y Laureles.</h3>\r\n<p>[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"\" row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" angled_section=\"no\" text_align=\"left\" background_image_as_pattern=\"without_pattern\" full_width=\"stretch_row_content\"][vc_column offset=\"vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs\"][vc_separator type=\"normal\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"tyc\"]*Las imágenes aquí contenidas son una representación gráfica del artista de cómo podría dotarse o usarse los espacios, y no debe entenderse como una reproducción exacta, detallada o a escala de los apartamentos, zonas comunes del edificio y elementos que lo integran. Los muebles, enseres, jardines, paisajes, objetos decorativos y de dotación que aparecen en las imágenes aquí contenidas, tienen un fin meramente ilustrativo y artístico y no deben entenderse como oferta o compromiso de entrega de los mismos, por lo tanto, se pueden presentar variaciones y modificaciones en materiales, acabados, colores, formas, diseño de elementos, dimensiones y texturas, entre lo ilustrado y lo entregado. Los inmuebles aquí publicados, y sus respectivas áreas privadas, pueden sufrir modificaciones como consecuencia del replanteo del proyecto, por disposiciones u órdenes de las autoridades públicas y urbanísticas competentes, o como consecuencia de caso fortuito o fuerza mayor. Las áreas de los inmuebles aquí publicitadas, corresponden al área total construida incluido el balcón, que es diferente al área privada la cual no incluye elementos que suelen ser áreas comunes de los edificios, tales como: muros estructurales, columnas, ductos, buitrones y muros de fachada. El estrato socioeconómico será el que defina la autoridad competente y está sujeto a cambio por parte de esta. El documento de especificaciones anexo al contrato de vinculación, contendrá las características de cada apartamento en concreto, los acabados del mismo y la información sobre dotación de las zonas comunes. Teniendo en cuenta que el edificio ya se encuentra construido a la fecha, el comprador podrá visitar el inmueble de su interés, el cual ya se encuentra terminado.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'Galicia', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'galicia', '', '', '2019-03-18 23:18:24', '2019-03-18 23:18:24', '', 0, 'http://m.constructoraguigo.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3, 1, '2019-03-18 22:37:02', '2019-03-18 22:37:02', '<!-- wp:heading --><h2>Who we are</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>Our website address is: http://m.constructoraguigo.com.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>What personal data we collect and why we collect it</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Comments</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor&#8217;s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Media</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Contact forms</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Cookies</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you have an account and you log in to this site, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select &quot;Remember Me&quot;, your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Embedded content from other websites</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Analytics</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Who we share your data with</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>How long we retain your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>What rights you have over your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Where we send your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Your contact information</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Additional information</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>How we protect your data</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>What data breach procedures we have in place</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>What third parties we receive data from</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>What automated decision making and/or profiling we do with user data</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Industry regulatory disclosure requirements</h3><!-- /wp:heading -->', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'open', '', 'privacy-policy', '', '', '2019-03-18 22:37:02', '2019-03-18 22:37:02', '', 0, 'http://m.constructoraguigo.com/?page_id=3', 0, 'page', '', 0),
